Building-

--Set CHARMHOME to your charm installation build on top of MPI
--Set FFT library to your fft lib
--make

Run-

--make test 
or
--mpirun -np <numprocs> ./fft_charm_mpi <fft size> <doValidate>
--mpirun -np 8 ./fft_charm_mpi 1024 1


The wrapper written in MPI "fft_charm_mpi.cc" parses input, creates
data arrays, initializes them, calls fft library in charm, and performs 
the validation.

